title: #92Noon!  10am Hour 8/16 - Arif Hasan
description: The Athletic's Arif Hasan stops by the studio and breaks down the X's & O's of what makes the 49ers such a great team, why Cam Dantzler has locked up a starting role on the Vikes defense, a potential Alexander Mattison trade, & much more!
